Rendering objectives:


Relieff techniques:
- Use gimp plugin to create normal and hightmaps
- Normal mapping (cookbook, anton, dhpoware)
- Parallax mapping (dhpoware)
- Alpha map (cookbook, anton)


Lighting:
- Point light (cookbook, anton, dhpoware)
- Directional light (cookbook, anton, dhpoware)
- Spot light (cookbook, anton, dhpoware)

- Multiple lights, standard (cookbook)

- Deferred shading (anton)
  - Displays different textures with keyboard 1, 2, 3 ... for QC.
- SSOA


